---
title: Sichuan-Glazed Meatball Rice Bowl with Soy Veggies & Pickled Onion
description: Discover a classic fusion of Asian flavours with a whole new twist! Take tasty garlic rice piled with moreish beef meatballs, all the right spices and tender veggies, and you’ve got a dinner-time hit. Serve with pickled onion for an extra punch of flavour.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sichuan-glazed-meatball-bun-cha-bowl-2e56e422.jpg
